いつもいつも当てつけては
Always, always being spiteful

354
00:24:05,065 --> 00:24:10,565
借りね 拙い 伺い ふざけないで
A debt, clumsy, an inquiry—don't mess with me

355
00:24:11,065 --> 00:24:16,565
言えない消えない思い込め 愛の完結アイスピック
With feelings that can't be said or erased, love's conclusion: an ice pick

356
