I hate you just because you're the person my crush likes

357
00:24:33,565 --> 00:24:38,565
都合の良い子 エディテイション 終わりたくないんだよ
A convenient girl, 'Edit-ation'—I don't want it to end

358
00:24:39,065 --> 00:24:44,565
狂った未来に迎合 終わった抵抗 いっそこのまま目塞いで
Catering to a crazy future, resistance is over—might as well keep my eyes closed

359
00:24:45,065 --> 00:24:50,565
切って爽快 喰らって崩壊 知って後快 望んだ将来
Cutting is refreshing, eating is collapsing, knowing is regret—the future I wanted

360
00:24:51,065 --> 00:24:56,565
手を繋いで 場を繋いで ファンタジックなすったもんだが
Holding hands, keeping the flow, a fantastic fuss...

361
00:24:56,865 --> 00:25:00,032
脳に感染 危険に発展 待ってこんな...
Infecting the brain, developing into danger—wait, this kind of...

362
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,390
