381
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:25,140
イヤイヤイヤイヤ
No, no, no, no...

382
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:29,840
やるせなくなっちゃうわ
woh-oh woh-oh-oh
...it just makes me feel helpless.
woh-oh woh-oh-oh

383
