言いかけていたことが一つ 消えてまた増えて
One thing I was about to say vanishes, then another appears,

494
00:33:38,373 --> 00:33:41,248
背中に後ろめたさが残る
leaving a sense of guilt behind.

495
00:33:42,373 --> 00:33:45,248
したがいたい心に 根を吐き出さぬように込めて
Rooting feelings of wanting to follow into my heart so they don't leak out,

496
